# Pursuit Bank SOP System - Code Owners
#
# This file defines who should review changes to SOPs and system components.
# When a PR is created that modifies files matching these patterns,
# the specified users/teams will automatically be requested as reviewers.
#
# Format: path-pattern @github-username @github-team
#
# More info: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# =============================================================================
# DEFAULT OWNERS
# =============================================================================

# Default owners for all files (fallback if no specific match)
* @sop-admin-team

# =============================================================================
# MORTGAGE FINANCE SOPs
# =============================================================================

# All mortgage SOPs require review from underwriting and compliance
/sops/mortgage/ @underwriting-team @compliance-team

