# =============================================================================
# NOTES FOR CODE OWNERS
# =============================================================================
#
# Responsibilities:
# - Review assigned PRs within 48 hours
# - Verify technical accuracy and completeness
# - Check compliance requirements
# - Validate training impact assessment
# - Ensure proper version increment and changelog
#
# Approval Requirements:
# - At least one approval from each required owner
# - Compliance officer approval for compliance-impacted changes
# - CFO approval for financial/treasury SOPs over $100K threshold
#
# Escalation:
# - If blocked or need expedited review: @sop-admin-team
# - For compliance questions: @compliance-officer
# - For technical issues: @devops-team
#
